title: YouTube mobile search drive Google Alphabet higher
text:
YouTube, mobile search drive Google Alphabet higher 
thestar.com Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Alphabet Inc., the company formerly known as Google, reported quarterly results Thursday that easily beat expectations on gains in mobile search and YouTube ad revenue, sending shares ahead by 11 per cent in extended trading.
